## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on gender inequality. The complexity of the issue means that factors contributing to gender inequality can vary significantly across different cultures and societies. Additionally, the sources used may not cover the most recent developments or emerging trends in gender equality efforts. Further research is needed to explore these aspects comprehensively.

